implements org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<IngressKeyType<VidType>>

Abstract MapKey for edge ingress templated with VidType. This key is a "union" type of two types: EdgeKey and VertexKey. The reducer calls different reduce methods based on the key type.

Field Detail

EDGEKEY

public static final short EDGEKEY
Enums of the map key types. EDGEKEY represents an intermediate edge record: (pid, (source, target, data)). VERTEXKEY is for a VertexRecord (vid, mirrors, inEdges, outEdges, vdata=empty). The reducer calls different reduce methods based on the key type.
